cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset, please cite it as below."
type: dataset
title: "VulnGym: a vulnerability-scene dataset with entry_point/critical_operation/trace annotations"
abstract: >-
  VulnGym is a curated benchmark of reviewed GitHub Security Advisories with
  per-entry-point entry_point, critical_operation, and trace annotations,
  intended for evaluating code-understanding and vulnerability-detection agents.
version: "0.1.1"
date-released: "2026-05-15"
license: CC-BY-4.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/<org>/VulnGym"
keywords:
  - vulnerability
  - dataset
  - benchmark
  - taint-analysis
  - security
  - LLM
  - agent-evaluation
authors:
  - name: "VulnGym maintainers"
